Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:02.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:04.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nfor our dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:07.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bird master Princess Abi\nbetrays Naraku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and thus begins\na three-way battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:17.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Furthermore, Kikyo has healed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and her reunion with Inuyasha\ndraws near!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new dayawaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I smell the birds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are we close to the nest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:16.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:20.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are Kikyo's shikigami!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}two....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those lights...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those {\i1}are....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:33.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soul Collectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's miasma which\nwas eating through my body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was purified by Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}still looks like she's in pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not completely healed yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must have noticed it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrier around the birds' nest\nis gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I could smell the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, what is Naraku\ntrying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's trying to get to the border
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,between this world\nand the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to get the Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:09.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he used the birds to\ngather human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which {\i1}means....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that the road that connects this\nworld to the afterlife will soon open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha {\i1}did....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he went after\ntwo young children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two young children...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}went to Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you and your friends intend to go to\nthe border between this world and the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're not gonna let someone like Naraku\nget his hands on the Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Then...\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,do not take Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The reason Naraku removed the\nbarrier around the birds' nest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was to lure you into his trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's goal is Kagome's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her power to see\nthe Sacred Jewel shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku wants to lure you\nto the border
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,between this world and\nthe afterlife
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and then force Kagome\nto locate the shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not completely healed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's impossible in your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:55.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My spiritual powers have\nnot weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll only end up\nas Naraku's prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is after your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Back then, {\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you were attacked\nat Mt. {\i1}Hakurei....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I refuse to give Naraku\na second chance at your {\i1}life....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never want to go\nthrough something like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll only be a {\i1}burden....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The arrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:55.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:56.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give this to Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But whether she can use it\ndepends on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something weird\nabout the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:42.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those {\i1}are....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They seem to be\nheaded somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:51.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now where did Inuyasha go\nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On top of which, it's morning\nand he's still not back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:57.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, the shikigami that\NInuyasha went {\i1}after....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know. Most likely,\nthey were Kikyo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Goodness! Of all the {\i1}times....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:07.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something scares me\nabout {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to stay sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}he wanted to see her alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still, what's the matter\nwith him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sneaking around like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, they're gonna\nstart fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't say\nsomething he shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I went to see Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He just came out and said it,\nwithout any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although, we know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She told me to give this\nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}Kikyo's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been rubbed with dirt\nfrom Onigumo's cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said it should be\neffective against Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What Kagome wants to know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is what happened between\nyou and Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't try to fool us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to fool anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I did was see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}just....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,wanted to see for myself that\nshe was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that really all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you upset, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not really.\NI trust you, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And {\i1}so....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me honestly\nwhat happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't believe me\nand she's angry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to stay sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they Naraku's demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I smell it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although it's very faint.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mixed into the smell of the birds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's evil aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:11:59.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, Jaken, will follow you any-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, wait! Please wait!\NLord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku removed the barrier\naround the birds' nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! It reeks with\nthe smell of the birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku wants Kagome's eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When we get to the\nother side of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you may face a bit of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you telling\nme such a thing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without me, you can't locate\nthe Sacred Jewel shard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reason Naraku removed the\nbarrier around the birds' nest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}was to lure you into his trap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it is Naraku's trap,\NI won't let it go his way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm right beside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll protect you without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay. I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then he's close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense a Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's in the birds' nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}Naraku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd\ncome looking for a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:34.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it payback time because\NI destroyed your castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess {\i1}Abi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your birds sucked out every drop\nof human blood at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:42.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And thanks to them, my mother\nhas been completely cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:53.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, my mother says\nshe wants to greet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is finally {\i1}opening....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The road that leads to the border\nbetween this world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:33.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what you are scheming,\nusing us in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:37.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, we no longer\nhave use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:06.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, it seems you chose\nthe wrong people to manipulate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't take me lightly, Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such attacks won't\nwork on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This will finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such puny flames won't\nbring down my barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll devour both you and your barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll swallow you in one gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is that the extent\nof your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's already at the nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!\NIt's his scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku removed the barrier\naround the nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and didn't send Kagura or Hakudoshi,\nbut went himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, the path that leads to the border\nbetween this world and the next
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is about to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what one would conclude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:55.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares what Naraku\nis scheming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:59.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we defeat him, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:16.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, is it true that\NNaraku is at Princess Abi's nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:21.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tekkei will be at the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga, who is Tekkei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tekkei belongs to a group\nof birds which live in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More precisely, she's a demon\nconnected to the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:39.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Tekkei is brutal, so\nyou must be extremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember, you have been warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And with {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So tell me, how do I\nget to the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that huge bird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tekkei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:09.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, have you all\ncome to die, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess {\i1}Abi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:20.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dead? Not that Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:27.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, that Naraku!\NHe's in my belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-So you ate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's probably hard to {\i1}digest....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe that Naraku\nwould be beaten so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:42.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, stay still and\nbe eaten by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as there aren't\nany saimyosho,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can use my Wind Tunnel freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:00.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:10.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:19.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:35.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A half-demon thinks he can\ndefy me and my daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:43.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is {\i1}this....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:45.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:19.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, how dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess Abi, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:36.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The trident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:48.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That trident was a part\nof my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have worked hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:21:00.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is your reward. You shall not\nsuffer when I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He takes every advantage\nof them, {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:20.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is nothing new,\nbut your methods are disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:32.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, weren't you planning\nto defeat Princess Abi, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to me, you all {\i1}are....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:45.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,now able to go to the border\nbetween this world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We chase after Naraku and cross\na river of blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and find ourselves at the border\nbetween this world and the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But suddenly, we're attacked\nby a spear of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:56.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit! The spear came\nfrom my old man's grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:59.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grave robbers who seek\nthe Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:00.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This eloquent {\i1}voice....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:01.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,could it be Hosenki?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:05.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The shard chose to come\nwith me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.53,0:24:09.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The Demon Protector of\nthe Sacred Jewel Shard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoever comes, I will not hand it over!
